# Cursor Project Rules

- Refer to `AGENTS.md` before starting any broad refactor.
- Absolutely NO hardcoded API keys or passwords in the codebase or git history. Use `import.meta.env` for environment variables.
- Ensure any visual changes test cleanly against mobile viewports.
- Always run `npm run build` as the ultimate smoke test before suggesting a push.
- Do not create scattered markdown guides. Update `docs/DEPLOY.md` or `docs/ADMIN.md` instead.
